Note=Borrowed (and adapted) from the ABA's Model Share Purchase Agreement.  

Law.Sec=<u>Governing Law</u>  All matters relating to or arising out of {this Agreement} or any transaction contemplated by {this Agreement} and the rights of the {parties} (whether sounding in contract, tort, or otherwise) will be governed by and construed and interpreted under the laws of {Dispute.Law.State.of} without regard to conflicts of laws principles that would require the application of any other law.
    